OL,3,C'Education is everything': Asylum
OL,4,Cseekers desperate for a chance to learn
OL,6,FSocial Affairs Correspondent Sarah
OL,7,FCorker and Senior Producer Lottie
OL,8,FKilraine report
OL,10,FITV News was granted rare access to
OL,11,Fmeet with the young refugees and
OL,12,Fasylum seekers at different stages of
OL,13,Ftheir pursuit for safety and an
OL,14,Feducation in the UK.
OL,16,FSiham's story: 'I just want to feel
OL,17,Fhuman'
OL,19,FSiham, who is 18, has been in the UK
OL,20,Ffor just a few months after fleeing a
OL,21,Fviolent civil war in Somalia.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/18
