OL,3,C'Education is everything': Asylum
OL,4,Cseekers desperate for a chance to learn
OL,6,FWhen we met her she was living in an
OL,7,Fasylum hotel in Yorkshire, having
OL,8,Fescaped the brutal conflict which left
OL,9,Fher with "no future and no chance of
OL,10,Fan education".
OL,12,F"I just want to feel human," she told
OL,13,FITV News. "The living in Somalia is
OL,14,Fpretty hard, we don't have safety, so
OL,15,Fthat's why I left to get a new chance
OL,16,Ffor living.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/18
