OL,3,C'Education is everything': Asylum
OL,4,Cseekers desperate for a chance to learn
OL,6,F"Even the girls in Somalia, they are
OL,7,F(treated) different because they are
OL,8,Fnot allowed to get work or education,
OL,9,Fgoing to school like normal people,
OL,10,Flike men."
OL,12,FSiham made multiple attempts to get to
OL,13,FBritain on a small boat, a perilous
OL,14,Fjourney that could have had fatal
OL,15,Fconsequences.
OL,17,FShe arrived to the UK in October, and
OL,18,Fis being supported by the Refugee
OL,19,FCouncil while she waits for her asylum
OL,20,Fclaim to be processed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/18
