OL,6,FShe dreams of one day going to
OL,7,Fcollege, something she could never
OL,8,Fhave done if she had remained in
OL,9,FSomalia.
OL,11,FFrequent moves between temporary
OL,12,Faccommodations make it harder for her
OL,13,Fto access a school or further
OL,14,Feducation place. For now she waits in
OL,15,Flimbo, to find out her future.
OL,17,FMotaz's story: 'I'm grateful to be
OL,18,Fwhere I am today'
