OL,3,C'Education is everything': Asylum
OL,4,Cseekers desperate for a chance to learn
OL,6,FMotaz escaped from Yemen with his
OL,7,Ffamily aged nine, eventually arriving
OL,8,Fin the UK as a teenager. His first few
OL,9,Fmonths were spent living in an asylum
OL,10,Fhotel.
OL,12,FWe met him, now aged 19, outside
OL,13,FGlasgow University where he had just
OL,14,Ffinished a morning lecture for his
OL,15,Fengineering degree.
OL,17,FMotaz, who has refugee status, faced
OL,18,Fbarriers throughout his education, but
OL,19,Fsays he is "grateful to be where I am
OL,20,Ftoday".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/18
