OL,3,C'Education is everything': Asylum
OL,4,Cseekers desperate for a chance to learn
OL,6,FThe fighting has left more than 19
OL,7,Fmillion people - over half of the
OL,8,Fpopulation - in desperate need life-
OL,9,Fsaving assistance such as food, clean
OL,10,Fwater, healthcare, and education,
OL,11,Faccording to Save the Children.
OL,13,FRecent discussions around refugees and
OL,14,Fasylum seekers arriving in the UK,
OL,15,Fincluding the government's sweeping
OL,16,Fproposals to overhaul the asylum
OL,17,Fsystem, has been "heartbreaking" for
OL,18,FMotaz.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/18
