OL,6,F"We are talking about people who are
OL,7,Ffleeing persecution, war, conflicts,
OL,8,Fhuman rights violations," he said. "We
OL,9,Fare talking about children, women,
OL,10,Fmen, people who want to rebuild their
OL,11,Flives and have a better future.
OL,13,F"When the media and politicians create
OL,14,Fa sense of uncertainty and insecurity,
OL,15,Fand it makes it difficult for local
OL,16,Fcommunities and people seeking asylum
OL,17,Fand refugees. It gives more
OL,18,Finstability and makes integration
OL,19,Freally difficult.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/18
