OL,8,Fthe guidance and support to make this
OL,9,Fplace home."
OL,11,FDaneshgar's story: 'Education is
OL,12,Feverything'
OL,14,FDaneshgar, who is in her 20s, is from
OL,15,FAfghanistan and had taught women and
OL,16,Fgirls to ride bicycles, an activity
OL,17,Fbanned under strict Taliban rule and
OL,18,Fsomething that nearly cost her life.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/18
