OL,3,C'Education is everything': Asylum
OL,4,Cseekers desperate for a chance to learn
OL,6,FUnable to return home, she made the
OL,7,Fdangerous crossing by small boat with
OL,8,Fher family in September to claim
OL,9,Fasylum in the UK.
OL,11,FNow housed in an asylum hotel, and
OL,12,Fsupported by the Refugee Council,
OL,13,FDaneshgar is determined to finish her
OL,14,Fdisrupted education and pursue a
OL,15,Fcareer.
OL,17,FWhen the Taliban seized back control
OL,18,Fof Afghanistan in 2021 the rights of
OL,19,Fwomen and girls in the country
OL,20,Fdisappeared almost overnight.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/18
