OL,3,C'Education is everything': Asylum
OL,4,Cseekers desperate for a chance to learn
OL,6,FUnder the harsh regime, women and
OL,7,Fgirls are barred from attending school
OL,8,Fand university, working in most jobs,
OL,9,Fusing spaces such as parks, gyms and
OL,10,Fsports clubs, and even speaking in
OL,11,Fpublic.
OL,13,F"When the Taliban took control,
OL,14,Feverything was destroyed for women,"
OL,15,FDaneshgar told ITV News.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/18
