OL,3,C'Education is everything': Asylum
OL,4,Cseekers desperate for a chance to learn
OL,6,F"You couldn't study, you couldn't
OL,7,Fwork, you couldn't do anything. I
OL,8,Ftaught women and girls how to ride
OL,9,Fbikes, it was not just for sport but
OL,10,Ffor women's empowerment. Because of
OL,11,Fthis me and my family's lives were in
OL,12,Fdanger."
OL,14,FDaneshgar is now waiting for her UK
OL,15,Fasylum application to be processed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/18
