OL,3,C'Education is everything': Asylum
OL,4,Cseekers desperate for a chance to learn
OL,6,F"Education is everything," she said.
OL,7,F"It is the most important thing. We
OL,8,Fwant to be in the education system as
OL,9,Fsoon as possible, we don't want to
OL,10,Fwaste time but you can't get a place
OL,11,Fat college."
OL,13,F'The asylum system dehumanises people'
OL,15,FIn November, the government announced
OL,16,Fradical reforms to tighten the UK's
OL,17,Fasylum system.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/18
