OL,3,C'Education is everything': Asylum
OL,4,Cseekers desperate for a chance to learn
OL,6,F"The system does absolutely dehumanise
OL,7,Fpeople," she told ITV News. "People
OL,8,Fare not a homogeneous bunch.
OL,10,F"They're from different conflicts,
OL,11,Fthey're fleeing persecution from
OL,12,Fdifferent countries, like in Sudan,
OL,13,Fthey're fleeing wars in places like
OL,14,FAfghanistan.
OL,16,FLaura Cooper, an asylum hotel support
OL,17,Fworker for the Refugee Council, told
OL,18,FITV News the current system 'lacks
OL,19,Fhumanity'
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/18
