OL,6,F"People are not all the same, but they
OL,7,Fhave been forced together to endure
OL,8,Fthis temporary living in a hotel," she
OL,9,Fadded.
OL,11,FThe government did not comment the
OL,12,Fissues raised about the barriers
OL,13,Ffacing asylum seekers and refugees
OL,14,Fover 18.
OL,16,FA Department for Education
OL,17,Fspokesperson told ITV News: "The
OL,18,Fgovernment is committed to
OL,19,Fsafeguarding the welfare of all
OL,20,Fchildren living in the UK, to ensure
OL,21,Fevery child has the best start in life.
