OL,3,C'Education is everything': Asylum
OL,4,Cseekers desperate for a chance to learn
OL,6,F"All school-age children in England
OL,7,Fare required by law to receive full
OL,8,Ftime education, regardless of their
OL,9,Fimmigration status, and state schools
OL,10,Fare expected to admit children on
OL,11,Fapplication.
OL,13,F"Councils receive funding to provide
OL,14,Fchildren's social care services for
OL,15,Fvulnerable children, and this includes
OL,16,Fchildren seeking asylum with their
OL,17,Ffamilies, and unaccompanied asylum-
OL,18,Fseeking children."
